2 An act relating to the Agency of Digital Services
3 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
4 Sec. 1. INTENT
5 The intent of this act is for the Agency of Digital Services to provide the
6 General Assembly and the public with more transparency about the scope,
7 budget, and overall status of certain information technology projects being
8 managed by the Agency. This act requires the Agency to include more details
9 about information technology projects it manages in its annual reporting as
10 well as on its publicly available website in the form of a current projects
11 inventory.
12 Sec. 2. 3 V.S.A. § 3303 is amended to read:
